events.title: Rescheduled Call on Epstein Case
events.description: A call originally scheduled for Friday is being rescheduled for Monday at 2 PM. Participants are coordinating dial-in information.

keyFacts: The document is an email chain dated July 1, 2019, concerning the Epstein case.
All participants appear to be from the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS).
The correspondence shows internal coordination to reschedule a call related to the case, indicating ongoing legal activity.
